  • Default DatePickers' value should be current date
  • Default selection view should be month

  • Admin can choose any date
  • Choosen date on DatePicker should be as choosen date each metadata

Currently, AccountBalance is stored as a part of a Payment entity. This story is about moving it to Staffer.

DOD

  1. AccountBalance is seen on the StaffPage as "Account Balance"
  2. AccountBalance is editable field and is saved with other Staff data
  3. Payments Page doesn't have AccountBalance column
  4. Payment is calculated using AccountBalance of appropriate Staffer
  5. Payment is calculated using AccountBalance valid for calculated date
